entries.femaleVariant: You want her to fall in love? Choom, gotta take her somewhere dangerous.
Really? Any suggestions? Dunno what's more her flavor – armed robbery in Kabuki or kidnapping in Vista…
Listen, I read all about it. Take her there, shit's gonna get intense, right? Got that stress, adrenaline pumping. So, like, she connects that feeling with you and – bam! – head over heels.
Oh, I know! Take 'er up to the top floor. Catch the Pacifica glow from there, even hear some gunshots. Danger's there, but it's far away... plus it's romantic as fuck.
Tellin' ya. Human nature, choom. Hormones. Can't fight 'em.
Uh-huh. So, uh, how's your output doin'?
Output? Nahh. Waitin' on the right girl.
